added.title: Teen Titans Vroom: Part 2
added.description: In the exciting conclusion of "Turbo Titans Go Force" the Titans must learn to work together to stop Dr. Military.

added.title: Teen Titans Vroom: Part 1
added.description: In this episode of "Turbo Titans Go Force" the Titans gain the ability to transform into cars.

added.title: Stop! Hamster Time
added.description: Owen takes over the job of caring for the class hamster and learns that he's evil.

added.title: Driving Miss Crazy
added.description: Duncan leads Beth to believe she's broken his battery-powered bike and makes her chauffeur him around in a wagon for the day as punishment.

added.title: Heat of the Moment
added.description: After Ben easily dispatches the Weatherheads, Team Tennyson travels to a ski resort for some fun in the snow but when Ben runs into the Weatherheads yet again, this time they are a force to reckon with, now that Kevin 11 has used his Bootleg powers to unlock their emotional controls!

added.title: Vin Diagram
added.description: When Ben sees Vin Ethanol impressed with Kevin's automotive know-how, Ben's jealousy has him convinced that he has to out-do Kevin before the older boy influences Vin to embrace his bad-guy side at a charity race.

added.title: You Remind Me of Someone
added.description: Ben and Gwen look for the infamous Bojamboo (the Bigfoot of the South) and discover that it's actually the Forgeti, at the same time as Kevin 11, but when Ben and Kevin are blasted with the Forgeti's forgetfulness mist, they reverse roles and it's up to Gwen and Max to restore them back to normal.

added.title: Adrenaland Jr.
added.description: Team Tennyson visits the safety-neutered version of Adrenaland known as "Adrenaland Jr.", only to end up facing off against a bitter Kevin 11, out to destroy everyone else's good, and safe, time.

added.title: Artesanias traviesas
added.description: Cuando, por accidente, Vic libera al señor de las travesuras del interior una reliquia antigua, V y V tienen que trabajar en equipo para volver a encerrarlo.

added.title: Futbol a Muerte
added.description: Cuando Vic no elige a Val para su equipo de fútbol, Val promete ganar con su propio equipo. Pero cuando su equipo no está a la altura, recurre a medios sobrenaturales para ganar.

added.title: Quintos Quinces
added.description: Victor y Valentino quieren ir a la fiesta en la piscina de un amigo el mismo día que la fiesta de quince años de su abuela, así que usan una flauta mágica que les permite teletransportarse y asistir a ambas al mismo tiempo.

added.title: La Leyenda del Parque Patinetas
added.description: Mientras buscan un parque de patinaje escondido, V y V se encuentran con una tribu de niños salvajes, que viven en una sociedad sin reglas ni adultos.

added.title: Amor de hermanos
added.description: Después de romper la planta de Chata, Vic y Val deben cumplir con la tarea aparentemente fácil de reemplazarla, lo cual demuestra no serlo cuando sus disputas ponen en peligro Monte Macabro.

removed.title: Chata's Quinta Quinceañera
removed.description: Vic and Val want to go to a friend's pool party on the same day as their grandma's quinceañera, so they use a magical flute that allows them to teleport and attend both at the same time.

removed.title: Folk Art Foes
removed.description: When Vic accidently unleashes the lord of mischief from an ancient relic, V and V have to work together to trap it back inside.

removed.title: Legend of the Hidden Skate Park
removed.description: While searching for a hidden skate park, V and V happen upon a tribe of wild kids, who live in a society without rules or adults.

removed.title: Dead Ringer
removed.description: When Vic doesn't pick Val for his soccer team, Val vows to win with his own squad. But when his team doesn't match up, he resorts to supernatural means to win.

removed.title: Brotherly Love
removed.description: After breaking Chata's plant, Vic and Val must accomplish the seemingly easy task of replacing it; this proves difficult when their squabbling puts Monte Macabre in jeopardy.

removed.title: Loteria
removed.description: Cuando Vic hace trampa en un juego de mesa encantado, los malvados personajes cobran vida, y V y V son los responsables de averiguar cómo volver a ponerlos en el juego.

removed.title: El club de los solitarios
removed.description: En lugar de celebrar el Día de San Valentín, Vic y Val se atreven a explorar una mansión encantada con sus rivales, Charlene y Piña.

removed.title: Huracan Chata
removed.description: Cuando V y V descubren que las emociones de Chata controlan el agua del lago, deciden sacar ventaja y comienzan su propio negocio de piscinas de olas.

removed.title: La ninera
removed.description: Vic y Val quieren colarse en un espectáculo secreto de fuegos artificiales, pero su plan se ve frustrado cuando su nueva niñera, Xochi, los supera en todo momento.

removed.title: Dia de limpieza
removed.description: Victor y Valentino adquieren un nuevo respeto por la limpieza después de que la casa de Chata los atrapa dentro de su laberinto de paredes antiguas y mágicas.

removed.title: Gnome More Mister Nice Guy
removed.description: When the daycare gets taken over by evil gnomes, Duncan finds himself on the wrong team.

removed.title: Look Who's Clocking
removed.description: When Harold's warnings not to mess with the clock go ignored, the kids are forced to save themselves when Duncan tears a hole in the fabric of time.

removed.title: Hurricane Chata
removed.description: When V & V discover that Chata's emotions control the water in the lake, they use it to their advantage and start their own wave pool business.

removed.title: Suerte
removed.description: When Vic cheats on an enchanted board game, the malevolent characters come to life, and it's up to V & V to figure out how to put them back in the game.

removed.title: The Babysitter
removed.description: Vic & Val want to sneak out to a secret fireworks show but are thwarted when their new babysitter, Xochi, outsmarts them at every turn.

removed.title: Cleaning Day
removed.description: Victor & Valentino gain a newfound respect for cleanliness after Chata's house traps them inside its labyrinth of ancient, magical walls.

removed.title: Lonely Haunts Club
removed.description: Instead of celebrating Valentine's Day, Vic & Val take on a dare to explore a haunted mansion with their rivals, Charlene & Pineapple.
